"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, my name's Scotty. I'm the owner of Scotty's Fermented Foods. Uh and the couple days ago I made a video telling you my business kind of struggling and I could really use some help if you could buy some of my food online at Scotty'sFoods.com like my traditional kimchi with fish sauce or my vegan kimchi, which is the same stuff without fish sauce, or even my white kimchi, which has no hot pepper in it. I'd really appreciate it. And y'all did. Y'all, I had overwhelming support. The video uh went nuts, and everyone commented, got a ton more views, and everyone shared it. And I received more orders that day, yesterday, than I did all month. And I really want to thank y'all and just share my appreciation with y'all because I was flabbergasted. I did not expect that. And I I learned a little something. You gotta show a human side when you're appealing to humans. It's not just about business. And so in the future I'm gonna do a little bit more of this. Anyway, thanks y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, my name's Scotty.\",\n      \"start\": 0.64,\n      \"end\": 2.8,\n      \"duration\": 2.16,\n      \"confidence\": 0.984,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.99\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.12,\n          \"end\": 1.28,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.28,\n          \"end\": 1.44,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.44,\n          \"end\": 1.6,\n       